diff --git a/CHANGES.rst b/CHANGES.rst
index 2db769f..be95f14 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -62,6 +62,11 @@ Unreleased
 -   Contexts created during shell completion are closed properly, fixing
     ``ResourceWarning``s when using ``click.File``. :issue:`2644` :pr:`2800`
     :pr:`2767`
+-   ``click.edit()``'s ``filename`` argument can now also be an iterable of
+    filenames, allowing multiple files to be edited at once in editors that
+    support it.
+-   Add ``process_priority`` parameter to ``click.edit()`` and ``Editor`` to
+    optionally set the CPU priority of the launched editor process.
 
 
 Version 8.1.8
